# Supabase Safety

- Generate SQL/RPC/RLS as drafts first.
- Explain security and data impact before applying migrations.
- Apply remote database changes only after explicit user approval.
- RLS policies require positive and negative tests.
- User-visible database errors should return stable error codes and be translated in the client.
- Service role keys are server-only and must never be used in Vite/browser code.
